{"id": "1405819042882650182", "channel_id": "1405815533676269640", "type": 0, "author_id": "1154601435141509192", "author_name": "jormiejormungandr", "author_bot": false, "content": "nope. naptime's not over. in fact, i am going to sleep on this event <:sleep2:1356085993626665200>", "timestamp": "2025-08-15T07:42:58.678000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "bow", "emoji_id": "1356053037159944473", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405815533676269640", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.1 广播剧《永燃不烬的追猎》┊Radio Drama - Everburning Hunt", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1405823400093679687", "channel_id": "1405815533676269640", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "**Everburning Hunt**\n\n**Kathigu-Ra**\nUgh, it's so damp in here... like a hot boiler. Makes my skin crawl...\n\n**\"Rox\"**\nHeh, just proves your rep's rock-solid, Big Sis. They got nowhere else to hide.\n\n**Kathigu-Ra**\nOh yeah? Look at you, all smooth all of a sudden. Should've sent you to deal with those old geezers.\n\n**\"Rox\"**\nWoah there, \"Claire,\" I was just tryin' to lighten the mood!\n\n**Kathigu-Ra**\nI'd rather hear: *'These sewer rats? Born to slither in the dark.'* That's more my style.\nWe're here.\nRitual Site of ▼▼▼—The Onyx Sacrificial Ground.\nSame old bloodstink. Let's see what we got...\nHollowed-out wax dolls, with guts carved clean. Faceless freaks, stitched-up chimeras, bone-flipped... plant pots?\nA ball of muscle... they stripped the skin and fused the muscles together with a branding iron?\nVocal cords are shredded. Guess they aren't fans of \"screams make the best offering.\"\nHuh. This sac’s... interesting.\n...They crushed the hard bits, pumped in fluid to cushion the guts, then stuffed it all into a pouch?\nIt says... *\"32nd Ritual Filling Material: LT-13. New process adopted, secondary material: DT-13...\"*\nThat's... the three underage kids of LT-13. These sick fucks never change.\nGood. Real good. Looks like I'm not leavin’ empty-handed this time.\nHeh, looks like the guards are here. Time's up, kiddos.\nMore of 'em than I expected, but...\nLucky for me, I'm just in the mood for some screaming!\nPlayed around too much. Shoulda kept one alive for directions.\n...Eh, whatever. Ain’t nobody walking outta here alive today. Plenty of time to take it slow.\nHm?\nBack already, kid? What’d you find?\nThat way? Got it. We’ll make sure your sacrifice ain’t forgotten.\nQuit yapping. If I said you're dead, then you're dead.\nNext party's gonna be your memorial. Make sure you bring a photo of yourself.", "timestamp": "2025-08-15T08:00:17.518000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🩷", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405815533676269640", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.1 广播剧《永燃不烬的追猎》┊Radio Drama - Everburning Hunt", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1405823461749948447", "channel_id": "1405815533676269640", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "**Kathigu-Ra**\n*(Heavy breathing)*\nDamn it, Rox, where are you?!\nRox's last signal cut out here...\n...No response. Ha. I'm flying solo now.\nC’mon, \"Claire.\" You must hold it together...\n\n**Cultist**\nBlasphemer against the New Dawn! You’ll feed our Lord’s altar!\nFoolish defilers... Rox and Claire, was it? Your flesh shall become the canvas for my sacrament—I will carve sigils of torment into your very souls!\n\n**Kathigu-Ra**\nOh yeah? Too bad. That kid’s soul’s already back with me.\nBesides, his name ain’t Rox, and mine sure as hell ain’t Claire.\n\n**Cultist**\nN-No! How? You're still alive?! With that power, why would you—", "timestamp": "2025-08-15T08:00:32.218000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405815533676269640", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.1 广播剧《永燃不烬的追猎》┊Radio Drama - Everburning Hunt", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1405823474387390526", "channel_id": "1405815533676269640", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "**Kathigu-Ra**\nTo give you what you want, of course. Isn't this your favorite? You love seeing the look of despair on your prey. Yeah, like the one on your face right now.\n\n**Cultist**\nAAARRRGHHHHH!\n\n**Kathigu-Ra**\nHah, you should be thanking me! Rejoice. I’m feelin’ generous today. It's so cathartic to torture scum like you.\nAs a reward, you get to enjoy a premium kind of pain, overflowing with malice and desire!\nCrush all of your bones, then pull half the fragments out of your body.\nI'll grind those bone bits and your eyeballs together, stuffing them right into your sockets.\nTear your skin and flesh, rub your exposed nerves, and rip them out in one go.\nNow my hot gun barrel is perfect for cauterizing the wounds and stop the bleeding... Haha, wouldn't want you to dry out yet.\nPour your body fluids into your airways, keeping you just on the verge of suffocating.\nOpen your skull, then stimulate your brain to keep you conscious.\nHeh, look at it from a distance... it's a real work of art. A perfect look for people like you.\nI guess that's enough for today. I'm getting bored.\nBegone, trash.\nNow... where’s that thing?\nHaha, here you are... Idol of the \"Faceless Chaos.\"\nTold you, rat. You're not hiding from me. Ever.\nFarewell, Mr. Rapture. Say goodbye to this scrap of your pathetic existence, filthy ▼▼!\nPhew, what a great day.\nAlright, kids. Naptime’s over.\nTime for a wake-up call! We'll burn it all to the ground! Every last guilty scrap!", "timestamp": "2025-08-15T08:00:35.231000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405815533676269640", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.1 广播剧《永燃不烬的追猎》┊Radio Drama - Everburning Hunt", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
